  <brief_title>Study to Evaluate the Effects of Kuvan on Individuals With Phenylketonuria (PKU) With Maladaptive Behaviors</brief_title>
  <official_title>Pilot Study to Evaluate the Effects of Kuvan on Adult Individuals With Phenylketonuria With Measurable Maladaptive Behaviors</official_title>
