  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To validate the outcome measures and the tolerability of Kuvan treatment in the improvement
      of behavioral symptoms in 10 selected adults with Phenylketonuria (PKU) with or without
      mental retardation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
